cificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade","id":"compatibilidade"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"O método toString() retorna uma string representando o objeto.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toString()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/tostring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object","title":"Object"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString","title":"Object.prototype.toString()"}],"pageTitle":"Object.prototype.toString() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}